		<DIV ALIGN="CENTER">
		
		<DIV ALIGN="CENTER"><FONT SIZE="+2">Sarnak Brains</FONT><BR>
Zone : Lake Of Ill Omen<BR><BR>
<TABLE CELLSPACING = 0 CELLPADDING = 0 BORDER = 0>
<TR><TD><DIV ALIGN="CENTER">
<TABLE WIDTH=410 VALIGN="ABSMIDDLE" HALIGN="ABSMIDDLE">
<TR><TD>
<FONT SIZE="1" FACE="ariel"><B>Added :</B> June 04th 2000</FONT><BR><BR>

<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="ariel">


This quest is a great way to raise faction with the guilds of Cabilis. Killing Sarnaks will raise your faction with the Legion of Cabilis(warriors/guards) but does not raise any other Cabilis factions. If you are at least dubious to the Legion of Cabilis you can use this quest to raise other Cabilis factions.<BR><BR> 

Warlord Geot can be found in the Lake of Ill Omen right next to the entrance to Cabilis. He is on the top floor of a tower so be wary. Shadowknights patrol out here and though you may not be KOS by the legion you might be KOS to them.<BR><BR>

Warlord Geot will reward you with a piece of food usually for every four Sarnak Hatchling Brains that you return to him. These brains can be found on the low level Sarnaks that patrol near by. Turning four brains in raises faction with LegionOfCabilis, CabilisResidents, ScaledMystics, CrusadersOfGreenmist, and Swifttails. Faction raises slowly though and it will take a LOT of work to raise from KOS to a more reasonable level.<BR><BR>

</FONT>
</TD></TR>
